{
  "stem": "9558.4",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And then they took out-- they took a German-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] --prisoner who was a big shot, with the red [INAUDIBLE] that means political prisoner.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So he took off my shoes, because I had a good pair of shoes, because I worked in the [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So for food, I could get a good pair of shoes.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But they took it off.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we walked 20, 30 below 0.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "If they shoot a guy, they took off his [INAUDIBLE], his uniform.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Everybody took a piece of [NON-ENGLISH], wrapped around our legs, and this is how we walked.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Then they put them in the movie theater.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In Europe was 200, 300 people, that was already a big theater.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They put in 2,000 or 3,000 because the SS wanted to go to sleep.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So they piled up 2,000, 3,000 people in a church, a movie theater.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And whoever was strong enough survived.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Whoever was underneath never survived.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Whoever was on top survived, because they put them in a small room like this, a few thousand people, where normally 200 people went in.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] That was the march.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I could talk about it for now-- they put us once into a tunnel, but there was no light on the end of the tunnel.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "The tunnel didn't go through.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Hundreds and hundreds and hundreds of people died there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I was looking-- I remember like the day I was looking for something sharp to cut my wrist.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And the last thing that I remember, I put my head down.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "It was water.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And I was lucky there was water, a little bit, so my head went there.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I fall asleep.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And in the morning, I woke up, so I heard they were yelling.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "They were pulling out from people there.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
